Class GenericMediaEvent

Direct Known Subclasses:
GenericResourceEvent
public class GenericMediaEvent
extends java.lang.Object
implements javax.telephony.media.MediaEvent, java.io.Serializable

This is the base media event class.

Currently it is serializable and provides for terminal-name construction so that it is possible for media service providers (RawProvider implementors) to create instances of these events as error events encapsulated within MediaResourceExceptions. Creation date: (2000-05-03 11:31:18)
